import sys
import os
import yaml
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
from datetime import datetime, timedelta

#    ( )
plt.rcParams['font.family'] = 'DejaVu Sans'

# filter.py   
sys.path.append(os.path.abspath('../src'))
from filter import DroneDataFilter

#   
with open('../src/config/filter_config.yaml', 'r') as f:
    config = yaml.safe_load(f)

# DroneDataFilter  
filter = DroneDataFilter(config)

try:
    #  
    processed_data, scaler_params = filter.filter_batch()
    
    # 1.   
    plt.figure(figsize=(15, 12))
    
    # IMU 
    plt.subplot(3, 1, 1)
    plt.title('IMU Angular Velocity')
    plt.plot(processed_data['angular_velocity_x'], label='x', alpha=0.7)
    plt.plot(processed_data['angular_velocity_y'], label='y', alpha=0.7)
    plt.plot(processed_data['angular_velocity_z'], label='z', alpha=0.7)
    plt.legend()
    plt.grid(True)
    
    plt.subplot(3, 1, 2)
    plt.title('Linear Acceleration')
    plt.plot(processed_data['linear_acceleration_x'], label='x', alpha=0.7)
    plt.plot(processed_data['linear_acceleration_y'], label='y', alpha=0.7)
    plt.plot(processed_data['linear_acceleration_z'], label='z', alpha=0.7)
    plt.legend()
    plt.grid(True)
    
    plt.subplot(3, 1, 3)
    plt.title('Position')
    plt.plot(processed_data['position_x'], label='x', alpha=0.7)
    plt.plot(processed_data['position_y'], label='y', alpha=0.7)
    plt.plot(processed_data['position_z'], label='z', alpha=0.7)
    plt.legend()
    plt.grid(True)
    
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

    # 2.  
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 10))
    numeric_cols = processed_data.select_dtypes(include=[np.number]).columns
    correlation = processed_data[numeric_cols].corr()
    sns.heatmap(correlation, annot=True, cmap='coolwarm', center=0, fmt='.2f')
    plt.title('Feature Correlation Heatmap')
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

    # 3. 3D  
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(10, 10))
    ax = fig.add_subplot(111, projection='3d')
    ax.scatter(processed_data['position_x'], 
              processed_data['position_y'], 
              processed_data['position_z'], 
              c=np.arange(len(processed_data)), 
              cmap='viridis', 
              alpha=0.1)
    ax.set_xlabel('X Position')
    ax.set_ylabel('Y Position')
    ax.set_zlabel('Z Position')
    plt.title('3D Flight Path')
    plt.show()

    # 4.    (boxplot)
    plt.figure(figsize=(15, 6))
    sensor_data = ['angular_velocity', 'linear_acceleration', 'position']
    for i, sensor in enumerate(sensor_data):
        plt.subplot(1, 3, i+1)
        cols = [col for col in processed_data.columns if sensor in col]
        processed_data[cols].boxplot()
        plt.title(f'{sensor} Distribution')
        plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

    # 5.   
    print("\nData Statistics:")
    print(processed_data.describe())
    
    # 6.    
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 5))
    sim_counts = processed_data['simulation_id'].value_counts()
    sim_counts.plot(kind='bar')
    plt.title('Data Points per Simulation')
    plt.xlabel('Simulation ID')
    plt.ylabel('Number of Data Points')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

except Exception as e:
    print(f"Error during visualization: {e}")
finally:
    filter.cleanup()
